OL,3,CNeil Simpson secures Great Britain's
OL,4,Cfirst medal at 2026 Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FNeil Simpson has claimed
OL,7,FParalympicsGB's first medal at the
OL,8,FWinter Paralympics 2026, earning
OL,9,Fsilver in the men's alpine combined.
OL,11,FHe and his guide Rob Poth were sitting
OL,12,Fin fourth place this morning, but
OL,13,Fgaining the quickest time in the
OL,14,Fslalom run elevated them to silver
OL,15,Fmedal position.
OL,17,FIt means Simpson now owns the whole
OL,18,FParalympic medal trifecta, after
OL,19,Fwinning a gold and bronze medal in
OL,20,FBeijing 2022, both with his brother
OL,21,FAndrew as guide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
