CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773216518
OL,3,CNeil Simpson secures Great Britain's
OL,4,Cfirst medal at 2026 Winter Paralympics
OL,6,FSimpson said he was "chuffed" with his
OL,7,Fperformance.
OL,9,F"The visually impaired men's is really
OL,10,Fstrong and there's lots of really
OL,11,Fgreat guys in there so really pleased
OL,12,Fto get on to the podium."
OL,14,FPoth said he felt the British pair can
OL,15,Ftake this confidence into the giant
OL,16,Fslalom event on Friday, with the
OL,17,Fslalom race following on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
