PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773216518
OL,3,CNeil Simpson secures Great Britain's
OL,4,Cfirst medal at 2026 Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"I'm buzzing with it to be honest," he
OL,7,Fsaid. "For me, it was a little bit of
OL,8,Fa relief, but I think our slalom is in
OL,9,Fa great place and I think we won that
OL,10,Frun."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn the women's combined VI event,
OL,18,FMenna Fitzpatrick, GB's most decorated
OL,19,FParalympic skier, finished in ninth
OL,20,Fplace with her guide Katie Guest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
