PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773216518
OL,3,CNeil Simpson secures Great Britain's
OL,4,Cfirst medal at 2026 Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"Every race that you do builds on
OL,7,Fconfidence. It adds little bits every
OL,8,Ftime," said Fitzpatrick. "It's more
OL,9,Fexperience in the start gate and it
OL,10,Fhelps calm the nerves as well. We know
OL,11,Fwhere to go for the next few races."
OL,13,FEarlier on Tuesday, Britain's mixed
OL,14,Fwheelchair curling team were beaten 8-
OL,15,F6 by hosts Italy, slipping to another
OL,16,Fdisappointing defeat in the round-
OL,17,Frobin stage.
OL,19,FHugh Nibloe's team will be back in
OL,20,Faction on Wednesday morning, as they
OL,21,Fface off against China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
