PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773216518
OL,3,CNeil Simpson secures Great Britain's
OL,4,Cfirst medal at 2026 Winter Paralympics
OL,6,F"We are going to come out and are
OL,7,Fgoing to do the very best we can. The
OL,8,Fpressure has left us now," said Nibloe.
OL,10,F"We have not been destroyed like other
OL,11,Fteams have been, so we have got
OL,12,Fpositives to take.
OL,14,F"It is an inexperienced team and some
OL,15,Fof these guys have more Paralympics in
OL,16,Fthem so let's see what it feels like
OL,17,Fto win again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
